    <title>Sewers and Urbanization in the Developing World</title>
    <updated>2025-03-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Sean E. McCulloch, Matthew P. Schaelling, Matthew Turner &amp; Toru Kitagawa</name>
