    <title>The Cybernetic Teammate: A Field Experiment on Generative AI Reshaping Teamwork and Expertise</title>
    <updated>2025-04-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Fabrizio Dell'Acqua, Charles Ayoubi, Hila Lifshitz, Raffaella Sadun, Ethan Mollick, Lilach Mollick, Yi Han, Jeff Goldman, Hari Nair, Stewart Taub &amp; Karim Lakhani et al. (View all)</name>
